                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030420-114-off615 t18030420-114-cd616"></join>, 40lb. of lead, value 10s. 6d. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18030420-114-victim897" type="victimName">
                        Matthew 
                        Easum
                     <interp inst="t18030420-114-victim897" type="surname" value="Easum"></interp>
